webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) The new church in Hannäs was built in 1884-85 after long discussion in both form and location. Architectural admiration for the exterior expression went to Albert Törnqvist and for the interior decoration of Ernst Jacobsson. The church was given the Gothic style that was ruling at the time - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMFB000591. AB Flygtrafik. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021016419905. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
